videos.description: Reggie Chaney throws down a big alley-oop with authority off the pass from Isaiah Joe.
videos.headline: Chaney throws down two-handed alley-oop

videos.description: Tyler Herro drains the long 3-pointer as the Wildcats shorten the deficit to 48-42 against Arkansas.
videos.headline: Herro drains long 3 for Wildcats

videos.description: No. 4 Kentucky comes back in the second half thanks to Tyler Herro's 29 points as the Wildcats top Arkansas 70-66.
